 <title>&kw-hos-tm; 5.0: Compute Service (Nova) Features</title>
 <para>
  Compute Service (Nova) implements services and associated libraries to
  provide massively scalable, on demand, self service access to compute
  resources, including bare metal, virtual machines, and containers.
